### Admin login (store token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUser}}",
  "password": "{{adminPass}}"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### List tires (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search tires (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires?brand={{brand}}&series={{series}}&size={{size}}&active={{active}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create tire (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "brand": "Bridgestone",
  "series": "ALENZA H/L 33",
  "origin": "日本",
  "size": "225/60 R18",
  "price": 3850,
  "isActive": true
}

### Update tire (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires/{{tireId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "brand": "Bridgestone",
  "series": "ALENZA H/L 33",
  "origin": "日本",
  "size": "225/60 R18",
  "price": 3900,
  "isActive": true
}

### Toggle tire active (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires/{{tireId}}/active
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isActive": false
}